== Kurekura ==
''2016'' yamenyekanye bwa mbere muri 2011 ubwo trailer yiyi firime yashyizwe kuri YouTube . ''Huffington Post'' yise iyo trailer"Bizarre and Wonderful",  igihe Cyriaque Lamar wo muri io9 yavuze ko "ahanini ari Alien, ''Inyamanswa'', na ''Terminator'' bose bazindukiye muri imwe".  Iyi trailer yerekanwe ku gice cya 2015 cy'ibiganiro bitinze nijoro ''Conan'', irimo umushyitsi TJ Miller .  Filime yacitsemo ibice bibiri, kimwe nibisanzwe ku isoko ryerekanwa na videwo muri [[Afurika]] y'Iburengerazuba.
